body_html: I'm afraid I can't build with this package in the Google environment, and you'll need to find someone in the open-source community to help you. Perhaps you can get some help on stackoverflow. It's a contrib package contributed by @jbedorf. Perhaps you don't have a full installation of MPI, or it's not an installation with which this package was tested.
